name: Elsa print- 11x14 premium matte
description:
Elsa and her sweet little owl.

Print is 11x14 (image size 10x13) on premium matte paper with a small white border for framing. Archival print made from an original oil painting by Marisol Spoon. Printed on premium matte paper with archival ink and is guaranteed to stay true for lifetime. Has a lovely richness about it!

All prints are signed, and will arrive safely packaged in a stiff mailer.
